      • copyTo

        public static void copyTo(java.nio.ByteBuffer src,
                          java.nio.ByteBuffer dest)

        Copies all remaining bytes from src to dest. This is done without modifying the src's position. However, the dest's position is updated.

        Parameters:
        src - the buffer to copy from. its position will not be updated.
        dest - the buffer to copy to. its position will be updated.

      • copyRemaining

        public static java.nio.ByteBuffer copyRemaining(java.nio.ByteBuffer src)
        Copies the remaining bytes form src to a new byte buffer. This is done without modifying the src position. The dest position will be 0.

      • copyRemainingBytes

        public static byte[] copyRemainingBytes(java.nio.ByteBuffer src)
        Copies the remaining bytes form src to a byte array. This is done without modifying the src position.
